MIPS: Netlogic: Support compressed kernel

Add SYS_SUPPORTS_ZBOOT and SYS_SUPPORTS_ZBOOT_UART16550 config options
for XLR and XLP.

Update boot/compressed/uart-16550.c to add UART port for XLR and XLP.

